Sensitive Group.title: Sensitive Groups
Sensitive Group.text: Consider reducing prolonged or heavy exertion. Watch for symptoms such as coughing or shortness of breath. These are signs to take it easier.

General.title: General
General.text: Air quality is acceptable; however, for some pollutants there may be a moderate health concern for a very small number of people who are unusually sensitive to air pollution.

insightTextLong: Seek  safe shelter immediately. Damaging winds, large hail and tornados very likely.
